&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>맨 마지막의 Events 항목을 보면 정상적으로 pull 했음을 확인할 수 있습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>정상적으로 띄우고 있는지 확인하기 위해서 curl pod을 이용해 접근해 보겠습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl run curl -it --image&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>curlimages/curl sh
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>deployment에서 띄운 pod의 ip는 172.17.0.4 입니다. 다음 명령어로 정상적으로 띄우고 있는지 확인합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>curl 172.17.0.4
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>정상적으로 띄우고 있다면 아래와 같이 출력됩니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>&amp;lt;!DOCTYPE html&amp;gt;
&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>&amp;lt;html &lt;span class="nv">class&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;writer-html5&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">lang&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;en&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &amp;gt;
&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>&amp;lt;head&amp;gt;
&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span> &amp;lt;meta &lt;span class="nv">charset&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;utf-8&amp;#34;&lt;/span> /&amp;gt;
&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span> &amp;lt;meta &lt;span class="nv">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;viewport&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">content&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0&amp;#34;&lt;/span> /&amp;gt;
&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span> &amp;lt;title&amp;gt;Welcome to example’s documentation! &lt;span class="p">&amp;amp;&lt;/span>mdash&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span> example 0.1 documentation&amp;lt;/title&amp;gt;
&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>...
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="2-serviceyaml">2. &lt;code>service.yaml&lt;/code>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>위에서는 pod을 이용해 cluster 안에 있는 pod의 내용을 확인할 수 있었습니다. 이번에는 service를 이용해 로컬에서도 볼 수 있도록 하겠습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>docker/deploy/&lt;/code>에서 &lt;code>service.yaml&lt;/code>을 작성해줍니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">apiVersion&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">v1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">kind&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">Service&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">metadata&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">sphinx-doc-svc&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">spec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">type&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">NodePort&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">ports&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">port&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">8000&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">targetPort&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">80&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">protocol&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">TCP&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">selector&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">type&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">app&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">service&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">sphinx-doc&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>apply를 합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl apply -f service.yaml
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>service/sphinx-api-svc created
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>정상적으로 됐는지 확인합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl get svc
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>NAME TYPE CLUSTER-IP EXTERNAL-IP PORT&lt;span class="o">(&lt;/span>S&lt;span class="o">)&lt;/span> AGE
&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>kubernetes ClusterIP 10.96.0.1 &amp;lt;none&amp;gt; 443/TCP 44h
&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span>sphinx-doc-svc NodePort 10.105.108.18 &amp;lt;none&amp;gt; 8000:30511/TCP 43s
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>다음 명령어로 ip로 접근할 수 있습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; minikube service -n default --url sphinx-doc-svc
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>http://192.168.64.2:30511
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>정상적으로 document를 보여주는 것을 확인할 수 있습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="3-ingressyaml">3. &lt;code>ingress.yaml&lt;/code>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>다음으로 ip 주소를 domain 으로 바꾸기 위한 ingress를 작성해 보겠습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>docker/deploy/&lt;/code>에서 &lt;code>ingress.yaml&lt;/code>을 작성해줍니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">apiVersion&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">networking.k8s.io/v1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">kind&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">Ingress&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">metadata&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">sphinx-doc-ingress&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">spec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">rules&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">host&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">docs.sphinx.com&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">http&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">paths&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">path&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">pathType&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">Prefix&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">backend&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">service&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">14&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">sphinx-doc-svc&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">15&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">port&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">16&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">number&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">8000&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>apply 해줍니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl apply -f ingress.yaml
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>ingress.networking.k8s.io/sphinx-doc-ingress created
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>정상적으로 됐는지 확인합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl get ingress
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>NAME CLASS HOSTS ADDRESS PORTS AGE
&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>sphinx-doc-ingress &amp;lt;none&amp;gt; docs.sphinx.com 192.168.64.2 &lt;span class="m">80&lt;/span> 49s
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;code>/etc/hosts&lt;/code>를 열어줍니다. (환경에 따라 &lt;code>/etec/host&lt;/code> 일 수 도 있습니다.)&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>sudo vim /etc/hosts
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>파일을 열고 가장 마지막에 minikube ip와 ingress에 작성한 도메인을 입력합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-vim" data-lang="vim">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">192&lt;/span>.&lt;span class="m">168&lt;/span>.&lt;span class="m">64&lt;/span>.&lt;span class="m">2&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">docs&lt;/span>.&lt;span class="nx">sphinx&lt;/span>.&lt;span class="nx">com&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>위와 같이 적고 저장 후 닫습니다.
&lt;a href="http://docs.sphinx.com/">http://docs.sphinx.com/&lt;/a> 를 들어가서 정상적으로 api document가 나오는지 확인합니다.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>minikube를 이용해 seldon 사용해보기</title><link>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/seldon/quickstart/</link><pubDate>Wed, 21 Apr 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/seldon/quickstart/</guid><description>
&lt;p>이번 포스트는 Seldon Core를 설치하는 법에 대해서 설명합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>사용한 k8s 환경은 minikube 입니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="1-install">1. Install&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>우선, minikube를 시작합니다&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>minikube start
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>그리고 helm을 이용해 seldon-core를 설치합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl create ns seldon-system
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&amp;gt; helm install seldon-core seldon-core-operator &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --repo https://storage.googleapis.com/seldon-charts &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --set usageMetrics.enabled&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">true&lt;/span> &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --namespace seldon-system
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>상태를 확인해 봅니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl get all -n seldon-system
&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>NAME READY STATUS RESTARTS AGE
&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>pod/seldon-controller-manager-559c567c9-9tj9w 1/1 Running &lt;span class="m">0&lt;/span> 11s
&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>NAME TYPE CLUSTER-IP EXTERNAL-IP PORT&lt;span class="o">(&lt;/span>S&lt;span class="o">)&lt;/span> AGE
&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>service/seldon-webhook-service ClusterIP 10.101.37.1 &amp;lt;none&amp;gt; 443/TCP 11s
&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span>NAME READY UP-TO-DATE AVAILABLE AGE
&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span>deployment.apps/seldon-controller-manager 1/1 &lt;span class="m">1&lt;/span> &lt;span class="m">1&lt;/span> 11s
&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span>NAME DESIRED CURRENT READY AGE
&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span>replicaset.apps/seldon-controller-manager-559c567c9 &lt;span class="m">1&lt;/span> &lt;span class="m">1&lt;/span> &lt;span class="m">1&lt;/span> 11s
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="2-sklearn-model">2. Sklearn Model&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>deploy에 이용할 모델을 만들어 보겠습니다.
모델을 생성하는 코드입니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="c1"># sklearn_model.py&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kn">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nn">joblib&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kn">from&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nn">sklearn&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kn">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">datasets&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kn">from&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nn">sklearn&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kn">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">svm&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">def&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nf">train&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">():&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">df&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">datasets&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">load_iris&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">X&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">y&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">df&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">data&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">df&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">target&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">clf&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">svm&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">SVC&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">clf&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">fit&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">X&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">y&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">joblib&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">dump&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">clf&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;model.joblib&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">14&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">15&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">if&lt;/span> &lt;span class="vm">__name__&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">==&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;__main__&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">16&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">train&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>실행 시켜서 &lt;code>model.joblib&lt;/code> 을 생성합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="3-pvc">3. pvc&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>pod에 모델 파일을 옮기기 위해 pvc를 생성합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>우선 minikube에 접속해서 폴더를 생성합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; minikube ssh
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&amp;gt; docker@minikube:~$ sudo mkdir -p /mnt/models/sklearn
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>그리고 생성된 경로를 바라보는 pvc를 생성합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># sklearn-pv-volume.yaml&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">apiVersion&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">v1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">kind&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">PersistentVolume&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">metadata&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">sklearn-pv-volume&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">labels&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">type&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">local&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">spec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">storageClassName&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">manual&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">capacity&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">storage&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">1Gi&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">accessModes&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="l">ReadWriteOnce&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">14&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">hostPath&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">15&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">path&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;/mnt/models/sklearn&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">16&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nn">---&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">17&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">apiVersion&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">v1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">18&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">kind&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">PersistentVolumeClaim&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">19&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">metadata&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">20&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">sklearn-pv-volume&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">21&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">namespace&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">seldon&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">22&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">spec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">23&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">storageClassName&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">manual&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">24&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">accessModes&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">25&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="l">ReadWriteOnce&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">26&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">resources&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">27&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">requests&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">28&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">storage&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">1Gi&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>생성 후 상태를 확인합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl create ns seldon
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl apply -f sklearn-pv-volume.yaml
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>persistentvolume/sklearn-pv-volume created
&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl get pv sklearn-pv-volume
&lt;span class="ln">6&lt;/span>NAME CAPACITY ACCESS MODES RECLAIM POLICY STATUS CLAIM STORAGECLASS REASON AGE
&lt;span class="ln">7&lt;/span>sklearn-pv-volume 1Gi RWO Retain Bound seldon/sklearn-pv-volume manual 53s
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="4-deploy">4. Deploy&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>이제 SeldonDeployment를 생성하겠습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>간단하게 SKLEARN_SERVER를 사용하는 deployment를 띄우겠습니다. 우선 아래의 내용을 &lt;code>deploy.yaml&lt;/code> 파일에 작성합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="c1"># seldom-deploy.yaml&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>apiVersion: machinelearning.seldon.io/v1
&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>kind: SeldonDeployment
&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>metadata:
&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span> name: iris-model
&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span> namespace: seldon
&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>spec:
&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span> name: iris-model
&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span> predictors:
&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span> - graph:
&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span> children: &lt;span class="o">[]&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span> implementation: SKLEARN_SERVER
&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span> modelUri: pvc://sklearn-pv-volume/
&lt;span class="ln">14&lt;/span> name: classifier
&lt;span class="ln">15&lt;/span> parameters:
&lt;span class="ln">16&lt;/span> - name: method
&lt;span class="ln">17&lt;/span> type: STRING
&lt;span class="ln">18&lt;/span> value: predict
&lt;span class="ln">19&lt;/span> name: default
&lt;span class="ln">20&lt;/span> replicas: &lt;span class="m">1&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>그리고 apply를 합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl apply -f deploy.yaml
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>상태를 확인합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; k get po -n seldon
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>NAME READY STATUS RESTARTS AGE
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>iris-model-default-0-classifier-6bb64c9588-5q8ck 0/2 Running &lt;span class="m">0&lt;/span> 18s
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="5-test">5. test&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>정상적으로 작동하는지 확인하기 위한 테스트를 해보겠습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>우선 서비스에 어떤 것들이 있는지 확인해보겠습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl get svc -n seldon
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>NAME TYPE CLUSTER-IP EXTERNAL-IP PORT&lt;span class="o">(&lt;/span>S&lt;span class="o">)&lt;/span> AGE
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>iris-model-default ClusterIP 10.96.166.74 &amp;lt;none&amp;gt; 8000/TCP,5001/TCP 89s
&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>iris-model-default-classifier ClusterIP 10.102.2.217 &amp;lt;none&amp;gt; 9000/TCP,9500/TCP 114s
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>이 중 &lt;code>classifier&lt;/code> 가 붙어있는 svc 가 predict를 담당합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>로컬에서 사용할 수 있게 포트포워딩을 해줍니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl port-forward -n seldon svc/iris-model-default-classifier &lt;span class="m">9000&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>Forwarding from 127.0.0.1:9000 -&amp;gt; &lt;span class="m">9000&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>Forwarding from &lt;span class="o">[&lt;/span>::1&lt;span class="o">]&lt;/span>:9000 -&amp;gt; &lt;span class="m">9000&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>inference할 데이터를 생성해보겠습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>다음 파일을 input.json에 저장합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;data&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;ndarray&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mf">6.8&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mf">2.8&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mf">4.8&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mf">1.4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">],&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mf">6.0&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mf">3.4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mf">4.5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mf">1.6&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">]&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">6&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">]&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">7&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">8&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>다음 명령어를 이용해 predict를 해봅니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; curl -H &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;Content-Type: application/json&amp;#34;&lt;/span> http://localhost:9000/predict -d @./input.json
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;data&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="o">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;names&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="o">[]&lt;/span>,&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;ndarray&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="o">[&lt;/span>1,1&lt;span class="o">]}&lt;/span>,&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;meta&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="o">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;requestPath&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="o">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;classifier&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;seldonio/sklearnserver:1.7.0&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">}}}&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;code>[1, 1]&lt;/code> 로 예측되어서 나오는 것을 확인할 수 있습니다.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>kubernetes에서 ghcr package pull 하기</title><link>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/kubernetes/kubernetes_ghcr/</link><pubDate>Wed, 03 Mar 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/kubernetes/kubernetes_ghcr/</guid><description>
&lt;p>kubernetes 에서 사용하는 image는 기본적으로 dockerhub에서 pull 된다. 기본적으로 Local에 있는 패키지는 사용하지 않는다.
회사에서는 도커 이미지를 dockerhub와 같은 곳에 public 하게 공유할 수가 없다.
그래서 github 에서 제공하는 (GHCR) GitHub Container Registry for Docker images 을 이용해서 도커 이미지를 관리하고 있다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>GHCR 을 이용하기 위해서는 github access key 가 필요하다. 우선 github access token을 발급 받아 보자.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="1-ghcr-을-위한-github-access-token-발급-받기">1. ghcr 을 위한 github access token 발급 받기&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>우선 github setting에서 deplotver settings / personal access tokens 로 들어간다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/k8s/ghcr/0.png" alt="그림-1">
여기서 generate new token을 누른다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/k8s/ghcr/1.png" alt="그림-2">
토큰 이름으로 ghcr-token을 입력하고 packages와 관련된 권한을 주고 token을 생성한다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/k8s/ghcr/2.png" alt="그림-3">
다음과 같이 토큰이 생성된다. 이제 이 토큰을 잘 저장해둔다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="2-kubernetes-secret">2. kubernetes secret&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>다음으로 kubernetes 에 secret 을 생성해준다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl -n &amp;lt;k8s-namespace&amp;gt; create secret docker-registry &amp;lt;k8s-docker-registry-secret-name&amp;gt; &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-server&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>ghcr.io &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-username&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&amp;lt;github-username&amp;gt; &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-password&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&amp;lt;github-personal-access-token&amp;gt; &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-email&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&amp;lt;email-address&amp;gt;
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>k8s-docker-registry-secret-name&lt;/code>: secret 이름&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>github-username&lt;/code>: github 유저 네임&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>github-personal-access-token&lt;/code>: 발급받은 토큰&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>email-address&lt;/code>: github 이메일&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>예를 들면 아래와 같이 사용할 수 있다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl -n default create secret docker-registry test-ghcr &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-server&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>ghcr.io &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-username&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>aiden-jeon &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-password&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&amp;lt;github-personal-access-token&amp;gt; &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-email&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>ells2124@gmail.com
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>정상적으로 실행될 경우 아래와 같이 출력된다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>secret/test-ghcr created
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="3-yaml-파일-작성">3. yaml 파일 작성&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>이제 deployment를 위한 yaml 파일을 작성한다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">apiVersion&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">apps/v1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">kind&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">Deployment&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">metadata&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">test-deploy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">spec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">selector&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">matchLabels&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">type&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">app&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">service&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">test-deploy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">template&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">metadata&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">labels&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">type&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">app&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">14&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">service&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">test-deploy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">15&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">spec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">16&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">containers&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">17&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">test-deploy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">18&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">image&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">ghcr.io/{user-name}/{package-name}:{package-tag}&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">19&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">imagePullPolicy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">Always&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">20&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">ports&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">21&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">containerPort&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">80&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">22&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">imagePullSecrets&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">23&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">test-ghcr&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>image에 ghcr 의 도커 이미지를 입력해주면 된다.
그리고 imagePullSecrets에 좀 전에 생성한 secret 의 이름을 입력하면 된다.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>